Navigate to the internal "hospital_app" folder.

Install virtual environment using the command: These steps are for Windows user
  pip install virtualenv

Create virtualenv:
  virtualenv env

Activate virualenv:
  env\scripts\Activate  

Install all the dependencies:
  pip install -r requirements.txt

Run main.py:
  python main.py    

Open the following link in the browser:
  http://127.0.0.1:8080/swagger-ui

